data.system_settings: Samsung Galaxy J7 Prime ~ Android 7.0 Nougat
data.expected_result: It should take you to the server and the reaction menu will be closed
data.short_description: Opening a server from a message's reactions list would keep the reaction menu open
data.steps_to_repro: - Find a message with reactions - Hold on the message - Click reactions to bring up the reactions menu - Click on someone to bring up their profile - Click the mutual servers tab - Click on a server that's not the server you found the message
